  77:../../CM7/Core/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_timebase_tim.c ****   /* Initialize TIMx peripheral as follow:
  78:../../CM7/Core/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_timebase_tim.c ****    * Period = [(TIM1CLK/1000) - 1]. to have a (1/1000) s time base.
  79:../../CM7/Core/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_timebase_tim.c ****    * Prescaler = (uwTimclock/1000000 - 1) to have a 1MHz counter clock.
